divs: Sighting Detailswent out on deck facing East. Light low in the sky caught my eye. Watched go over thinking it was an airplane headed for DIA. I see and hear many airplanes as I am in a flight path. Suddenly the light just blinked out. There was no noise no navigation lights for it to be so low. Airspace is crowded and navigation light would have had to be on. NO SOUND. No navigation light or strobes. very strange.
